中共禁片, 豪一次比佢無咩所謂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:10:45.000Z","msg":"唔係優先場先係咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:12:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191201/20816722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191201%2F20816722&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipfxY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=c43ce0fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191201%2F20816722&h=028cb179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191201/20816722</a><br />\n<br />\n 2019年12月01日<br />\n《返校》港院商疑自我審查 <br />\n<br />\n《返校》改編自同名電腦遊戲，故事講述1962年的台灣實施軍法管治日日戒嚴，市民生活在白色恐怖之下，當年收藏禁書、讀禁書等同叛國罪，學校有負責思想控制的軍訓教官，學生跟老師人心惶惶。近日香港逆權運動爆發，社會情況跟《返校》不謀而合，如憲兵毒打學生、限制學生人身自由等，故電影在港上映一波多折，就有傳片商因擔心有人將逆權運動與該片劇情混為一談，原先預定10月上映忽然被抽起。然後《返校》排在今周四上映，<strong>但未知院商是否出於自我審查，而不敢排片，只有六間戲院安排映期。</strong>"},{"pid":"f02e66c25d8fe9bd70259fb811428a4bdc65952a","tid":1763588,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"636e52b52b235420606a120e2c18122bc76e62d3","tid":1763588,"uid":113185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2292d92f691ac4c04b165e020fc797f4490c9a97","tid":1763588,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b2eaa381f8227f3b5be792b382dbe10c300090f0","tid":1763588,"uid":113185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:06:11.000Z","msg":"優先場係Cinema City，唔好幫藍百鳴洗黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:07:36.000Z","msg":"套戲基本上得cinema city 做<br />\n大部分院商(包括百老匯, UA)都唔上....<br />\n<br />\n我覺得, cinema city 今次播中共禁片, 豪一次比佢無咩所謂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:12:09.000Z","msg":"梳尻，唔知原來真